(Grimm, 1877) b RGM.961900, 
<taxonomicName class="Bivalvia" family="Cardiidae" genus="Didacna" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Didacna eichwaldi" order="Cardiida" pageId="9" pageNumber="40" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="eichwaldi">Didacna eichwaldi</taxonomicName>
(Krynicki, 1837), same locality. Scale bar: 1 cm.
</paragraph>
